title.en: Welcome to my Sonolus Snake Game

description.en:
First of all, Thank You so much for trying my simple Snake game!

This basic Snake game, is actually my very first proper and "big" coding project, and it has been pretty fun to make!

While I consider this project finished, it might still have some bugs. If you want to report them, feel free to contact me on Discord.

Have fun while playing!
